<p>The injury has badly affected my training because I can't run (or walk sometimes) for a few days after a run. But, in total, I have run 228 miles while training for this marathon. I haven't lost any weight. In fact, I think I may have put on half a stone (that's not supposed to happen!) I will be there at the start and, hopefully, at the finish as well (many hours later).</p>
